    "body": "Hello folks, can I use this approach in the meantime?\r\n```js\r\nconst beforeBalance = ethers.utils.formatEther(await ethers.provider.getBalance(contract.address));\r\n// Run transaction to change balance\r\nconst afterBalance = ethers.utils.formatEther(await ethers.provider.getBalance(contract.address));\r\n\r\nexpect(Number(afterBalance)).to.be.lessThanOrEqual(Number(beforeBalance));\r\n```\r\n\r\nPlease let me know and thanks for your support! <3",
